messages.speech: The graduate trainee schemes are targeted at mainly fresh graduates.

Whilst we have taken in trainees with some work experience in the past, do note that salaries will only commensurate with the local market rates for a fresh graduate rather than your work experience. If you have been working for a number of years, you may want to consider if this is the right scheme for you.
